description:
Our place is close to Saggio, Le Chéile, 181 Cabrini, Starbucks, Dunkin Donuts, Dominos. You’ll love our place because of the comfy bed, the coziness, huge living room with pullout couch. Our place is good for couples and families (with kids).

Living Room includes 55 in. TV, Apple TV, Xbox One, Blu-Ray Player, Roku, Pull Out Couch

Kitchen includes Microwave, Oven, Ninja
